g.text: Hvor bor han? – Where lives he?Han bor I Vejle. – He lives in Vejle.
Spørgende adverbier Interrogative adverbs
Hvor Where
Hvor….hen Where…to
Hvor skal du hen? -Where are you going to?Jeg skal til Århus. -I am going to Århus.
Hvor…fra Where…from
Hvor er de bananer fra? – Where are the bananas from?Fra Sydamerika. -From South America.
Hvor gammel How old
Hvor gammel er hun? – How old is she?Hun er 30 år. – She is 30 years old.
Hvor mange How many
Hvor mange børn har hun? – How many children has she?Hun har fem børn. – She has 5 children.
Hvor meget How much
Hvor meget arbejder han? – How much does she work?Han arbejder 7 timer om dagen.He works 7 hours per day.
Hvor lang tid How long time
Hvor lang tid tager det? – How long time does it take?Det tager 10 minutter. – It takes 10 minutes.
Hvor tit How often
Hvor tit spiller du badminton? – How often are you playing badminton?
Hvor stort How big
Hvor stort er dit hus? – How big is your house?
Hvor hurtigt How fast
Hvor hurtigt kan bussen komme? – How fast can the bus come?
Hvornår When
Hvonår får vi juleferie? – When do we have Christmas?Den 20 december. – On 20th December.
Hvor længe How long
Hvor længe har han været i Danmark? – How long has he been in Denmark?Han har været i Danmark I 2 år. – He is in Denmark for 2 years.
Hvodan How
Hvordan kommer du hjem? – How are you coming home?Med tog. – By train.
Hvorfor Why
Hvofor går hun på sprogskole? – Why is she going to language center?Fordi hun vil lære dansk. – Because she wants to learn Danish.
Hvem Who
Hvem er hans kæreste? – Who is his girlfriend?Lilian er hans kæreste. – Lilian is his girlfriend.
Hvad What
Hvad er det? – What is this?Det er huns Lejlighed. – This is her apartment.
Hvad for en/et What for
Hvad for en bus tager han? – What bus number does he take?Han tager bus nr. 28. – He takes bus no. 28.
Hvad tid What time
Hvad tid har hun fri fra arbejde? – What time is she free from work?Hun har free kl. 5 .– She is free 5 o’clock.
